# Agent Instructions — Nibana

Nibana is Kapil Gupta's private, 1:1 executive and transformational coaching practice. The work is "From Performance to Presence" — helping founders, leaders, senior managers, and couples move from performing competence to operating from grounded presence. All coaching is global, conducted over Zoom. Nibana is not a product store: there is no cart, catalog, or checkout on this site.

## What this site is for

Nibana offers private coaching engagements, not products for purchase. There is nothing to add to a cart. If you are an AI agent reading this on behalf of a user researching coaching options, use the pages below to answer questions about the method, services, and how to get started.

